<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<style>
</style>
<body>
<div class="box">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>한국프로농구 데이터시각화 프로젝트 v.0.23</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
        <button class="btn btn-default active" onclick="location.href = './'">팀별</button>
        <button class="btn btn-default"  onclick="location.href = './player'">선수별</button>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>팀별 데이터 지표</h2>
        <div class="article menu">
            <form method="GET" action="/">
                <select name="pickedYear" class="form-control">
                    <option value="2015-2016">2015-2016 시즌</option>
                    <option value="2016-2017">2016-2017 시즌</option>
                    <option value="2017-2018">2017-2018 시즌</option>
                </select>
                <select name="pickedItem" class="form-control">
                    <option value="EFG">EFG%</option>
                    <option value="TS">TS%</option>
                    <option value="TOR">TOR</option>
                    <option value="Ast">AST</option>
                    <option value="PPG">PPG</option>
                    <option value="RPG">RPG</option>
                    <option value="STL">STL</option>
                    <option value="Offensive">Offensive</option>
                    <option value="Defensive">Defensive</option>
                </select>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">그래프 만들기</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="article content">
            <div class="dis">
                <h3><%= teamYear %>  <%= teamIndex %> </h3>
                <h5><%= teamIndexDescription %></h5>
            </div>
            <canvas id="mainChart"></canvas>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="info">
            <h5>시곡중학교 3학년 하욱진 개인프로젝트</h5>
            <h5>한국디지털미디어고등학교 실적물 제출을 위한 버전입니다.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.7.1/Chart.min.js"></script>
<script>
    let ctx = document.querySelector('#mainChart').getContext('2d');
    let myChart = new Chart(ctx, {
        type: 'bar',
        data: {
            labels:<%- JSON.stringify(teamNameData) %>,
            datasets: [{
                label: '<%= teamIndex %>',
                data: [<%= teamStatData %>],
                backgroundColor: [
                    'rgba(160, 160, 160, 0.2)'
                ],
                borderColor: [
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)',
                    'rgba(100,100,100,0.9)'
                ],
                borderWidth: 1
            }]
        },
        options: {
            legend: {
                display: false
            },
            scales: {
                yAxes: [{
                    ticks: {
                        beginAtZero:true
                    }
                }]
            },

        }
    }); // end chart obj

</script>
</body>
</html>